<div style="text-align:center">

	<table border="0" style="width:800px;margin:auto;text-align: left; -moz-font-feature-settings:'liga=1, dlig=1'; -moz-font-feature-settings:'liga', 'dlig'; -ms-font-feature-settings:'liga', 'dlig'; -o-font-feature-settings:'liga', 'dlig'; -webkit-font-feature-settings:'liga', 'dlig'; font-feature-settings:'liga', 'dlig';">
		<tr>
			<td>
			<div style="width:100%;background-color:rgb(0,177,217);height:196px;text-align: center">
				<div style="text-align: left;margin:auto;width:686px">
					<img src="{$site}/portal/application/images/skills_header.png" style="margin-top: 36px"/>
				</div>
				{if $fname }
					<div style="margin-top:14px;margin-bottom:13px;text-align: left;width:686px;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;font-size:37px;color:#00B1D9;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-weight:bold;text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; ">Hi {$fname},
					</div>
				{else}
					<div style="margin-top:14px;margin-bottom:13px;text-align: left;width:686px;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto"><img src="{$site}/portal/application/images/hi.png" />
					</div>
				{/if}
				<div style="text-align:left;width:686px;margin:auto">
					<p style="margin-bottom:15px;font-size:14px;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color:#242424">
						<strong>Thanks for registration as a Remote Staff jobseeker.
						<br/>
						This is to acknowledge your application. </strong>
					</p>
					<p style="margin-bottom:15px;font-size: 14px;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
						To further process your application, please take at least 1 industry proven skills test to prove your skills level. Taking a test will not only help you ascertain your skills for personal assessment but will also help us in matching you to the right work from home position.  Applicants who take at least 1 skills tests are prioritized for processing. <strong>You can take as many tests as you desire.</strong>
					</p>
					<p style="margin-bottom:15px;font-size: 14px;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color:#415A60;font-size:24px;font-weight: bold">
						To take a Skills Tests,
					</p>
					<p style="margin-bottom:15px;font-size:18.67px;text-indent:32px;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
						Please log in as a job seeker at <a href="http://remotestaff.com.au/portal/">www.remotestaff.com.au/portal/</a>.
					</p>
					<p style="margin-bottom:15px;text-align:center"><img src="{$site}/portal/application/images/login.png"/>
					</p>
					<p style="margin-bottom:15px;font-size:18.67px;text-indent:32px;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
						Click on Skills Test Tab and begin to choose the test you want to take.
					</p>
					<p style="margin-bottom:15px;text-align:center"><img src="{$site}/portal/application/images/skill_list.png"/>
					</p>
					<p style="margin-bottom:15px;font-size:14px;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
						We will be notified after you take the test and you will hear from us within 2 business days.
					</p>
					<p style="margin-bottom:0;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
						We hope to hear from you soon!
					</p>

				</div>
				<div style="text-align: right">
					<img src="{$site}/portal/application/images/rs_logo.png"/>
				</div>
			</div></td>
		</tr>
	</table>

</div>
